"""
    start_device_discovery(discovery_type)
    start_device_discovery(discovery_type, params::Dict{String,<:Any})

This API is used to start device discovery for hub-connected and third-party-connected
devices. The authentication material (install code) is delivered as a message to the
controller instructing it to start the discovery.

# Arguments

- `discovery_type`: The discovery type supporting the type of device to be discovered in the
  device discovery task request.

# Optional Parameters

Optional parameters can be passed as a `params::Dict{String,<:Any}`. Valid keys are:

- `"AccountAssociationId"`: The identifier of the cloud-to-cloud account association to use
  for discovery of third-party devices.

- `"AuthenticationMaterial"`: The authentication material required to start the local device
  discovery job request.

- `"AuthenticationMaterialType"`: The type of authentication material used for device
  discovery jobs.

- `"ClientToken"`: An idempotency token. If you retry a request that completed successfully
  initially using the same client token and parameters, then the retry attempt will succeed
  without performing any further actions.

- `"ConnectorAssociationIdentifier"`: The id of the connector association.

- `"ConnectorDeviceIdList"`: Used as a filter for PLA discoveries.

- `"ControllerIdentifier"`: The id of the end-user's IoT hub.

- `"CustomProtocolDetail"`: Additional protocol-specific details required for device
  discovery, which vary based on the discovery type.

  !!! note
      For a `DiscoveryType` of `CUSTOM`, the string-to-string map must have a key value of
      `Name` set to a non-empty-string.

- `"EndDeviceIdentifier"`: The unique id of the end device for capability rediscovery.

  !!! note
      This parameter is only available when the discovery type is
      CONTROLLER_CAPABILITY_REDISCOVERY.

- `"Protocol"`: The protocol type for capability rediscovery (ZWAVE, ZIGBEE, or CUSTOM).

  !!! note
      This parameter is only available when the discovery type is
      CONTROLLER_CAPABILITY_REDISCOVERY.

- `"Tags"`: A set of key/value pairs that are used to manage the device discovery request.
"""
function start_device_discovery end

function start_device_discovery(
    DiscoveryType; aws_config::AbstractAWSConfig=current_aws_config()
)
